    	<h2><a name="2003-05-27" href="#2003-05-27"><font color="#660000">2003-05-27</font></a></h2>
   	

	<div class="posts">
	<a name="94952690">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://www.computerworld.com/printthis/2003/0,4814,81402,00.html">Security conference offers weird, woeful predictions - Computerworld</a>.&nbsp; The expectation of major IT "disasters" as well as problems with WIFI Internet technology and corporate privacy/security are strong messages.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#94952690">Tuesday, May 27, 2003</a></span></div>
<br>
  <!-- 2002-11-08 Change date format to yyyy-mm-dd and bookmark it 
